{"tid":2400272,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有香港貨輪同日本潛艇相撞","createTime":"2021-02-08T23:09:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T03:38:48.000Z","uid":19287,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"8e3a5373b2677e02fb9240db7dcf16cb140efdfb","tid":2400272,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T23:09:49.000Z","msg":"日本海上自衛隊的蒼龍號潛艇在高知県足摺岬外海於潛望鏡深度上浮時跟香港籍的鴻通號貨船（Ocean Artemis）相撞，艦上3人受輕傷。從海上保安廳Saab 340B巡邏機的視角可見，相撞點位於帆罩和前方水平翼，兩者嚴重損壞。此外，由於通訊桅桿損壞的關係，蒼龍號只能在3小時後以自身動力航行到有手機訊號的地方跟總部聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1685391655011370/posts/2847599688790555/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1685391655011370%2Fposts%2F2847599688790555%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMC3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=6b5420b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1685391655011370/posts/2847599688790555/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"fd20029413e1cdd062ec61dd52e28b4647d6e4fe","tid":2400272,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":73,"score":-73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T23:12:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d0468ba52b6874e738075706df0735267e0b137","tid":2400272,"uid":52215,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T23:17:39.000Z","msg":"架仔渣架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5a924b00d91e81bcc7ab5b1eb167e2a56e58f7b","tid":2400272,"uid":226655,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T23:19:44.000Z","msg":"部船咁大部都撞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9642236a32b345340e92635c7065e47ac5efcb9","tid":2400272,"uid":296700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T23:24:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25beebee4dabbcb90fb8e253c46a8410ad66a015","tid":2400272,"uid":32473,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"re